<emphasis id="C6CF800FCE62450E2038D3C3A8701E02" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="29">Figure 1.</emphasis>
General morphology of 
<taxonomicName id="712AAAF7C75CC9BB0E5111A3C7F17DA5" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Vitaceae" genus="Vitis" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Vitis adenoclada" order="Vitales" pageId="0" pageNumber="29" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="adenoclada">
<emphasis id="6893D54112AFC50D17BA1B6741F092A7" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="29">Vitis adenoclada</emphasis>
